{"tid":1251663,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"（不如不變）改詞不如不見","createTime":"2019-06-22T15:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T07:12:06.000Z","uid":216662,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef45c1f9cfef58c056f83288c6c5ea191db0585f","tid":1251663,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:39:33.000Z","msg":"捱煙彈 無可避免 來金鐘堅守血濺<br />\n齊衝擊 抵禦著警線 全城為惡法撕裂<br />\n<br />\n來支撐 黃色小傘 齊抵擋黑警那天<br />\n民意律法早被污染 還望這家園不變<br />\n<br />\n為理念上路然後發現<br />\n火種散落已蔓延<br />\n抗爭永不退後 堅決磨練<br />\n香港 總會有明天<br />\n<br />\n淚與汗撒落 猶像表演<br />\n青春耗盡那十年<br />\n抗爭哪些歲月 忽爾明白<br />\n港英這往事 年月在更遷 不如不變"},{"pid":"752a204f0f55d1484a891e994806b55e7a2611bf","tid":1251663,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5nLXMc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5nLXMc.jpg&h=5095f61d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n若若一推"},{"pid":"beff5013fdb38f35d8b1844a4de3fb49d8352920","tid":1251663,"uid":195485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"老實咁講...有啲怪"},{"pid":"4c09c5684ff1102710108544bd53d0664c1c55ac","tid":1251663,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beff5013fdb38f35d8b1844a4de3fb49d8352920","tid":1251663,"uid":195485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"老實咁講...有啲怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:48:29.000Z","msg":"唱咗兩句，放唔到上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1c35ffbfa3c44a5654e124a46a59048c06a216","tid":1251663,"uid":195409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"最尾果句好唔順"},{"pid":"2fd813e6f42cd5c8c6a4790f663a5e3bd6dba919","tid":1251663,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee1c35ffbfa3c44a5654e124a46a59048c06a216","tid":1251663,"uid":195409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22